Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.59,0:00:04.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.80,0:00:06.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.55,0:00:09.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret Technique: Tentacle Cannon!{奥義　触手カノン}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:14.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:16.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a brother waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:52.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:56.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You canned yourself into your room all morning during the weekend playing eroge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:58.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who forced me to play it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:02.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look down on me! You should be praising me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:04.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the spitting image of an erogamer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:05.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a compliment!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:08.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So? Have you cleared it once at least?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:11.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:18.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This game's special feature is the ability to use the character from your cleared saved game in a fighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:21.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you still haven't completed it, you can't play against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:23.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go fight with someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:25.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you do it online?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:27.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't win online.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.63,0:02:31.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go find a walkthrough site.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:35.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think I set it up so you can use the internet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:40.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The SisCaly ATWiki is really detailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:44.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Read it and spend all tomorrow clearing the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:45.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's even a Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:47.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, fine fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:50.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to clear it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:51.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.86,0:02:54.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I forgot to mention...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:57.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have friends coming over tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:59.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you don't come out of your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:03.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're cute, but if you try to talk to them, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:04.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even look at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:05.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll contaminate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:08.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I give a damn about your friends in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:15.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:16.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:31.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I can login?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:32.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this her character?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:45.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:47.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to give up! {check}{Perfect.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:52.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good day, Kiririn-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:55.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have a moment, would you like to chat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:59.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a totally different person online.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:03.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyousuke-onii-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.31,0:04:04.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:06.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:10.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's{\i0} doing too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for looking out for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:12.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:16.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm able to put Kiririn-san to good use in this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:18.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:21.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've managed to maintain an 8:1 win ratio.{FOTC: "Maintain" might be better.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:24.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the reason she's so moody...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:27.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you show me the ropes for this game then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:30.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's forcing me to play this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:34.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I figure if I can get good at it, I can beat her as revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's lovely to see you two getting along so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:39.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:42.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:46.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case then I'll walk you through it over the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:50.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Totally different person!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:05.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:08.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:09.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Heya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:10.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can just head upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:12.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring some drinks up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:17.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to intrude.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:24.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:28.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:31.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to stay in your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:35.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I seriously don't want you running into them, so hurry up and go to your room!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:37.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:42.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, if you go up now, they might see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:44.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with your brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:55.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see your phone then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:08.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:09.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an invasion of privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:11.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:13.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just admit it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:16.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I don't have a boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:19.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've been acting weird recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:22.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wh-What do mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.74,0:06:24.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:25.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That character you're putting on is so gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:29.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you talking on your phone one time, and you sounded really angry, but you looked kind of happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:31.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And after hanging up you had this huge smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.54,0:06:32.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely a boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:35.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:41.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, stop already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:44.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a boyfriend or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:47.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The goosebumps!! She's making me sick!! {this pose is hilarious}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:50.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:54.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, the person downstairs was your brother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:57.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you look so annoyed all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:00.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks like a kind brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to see an optometrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:04.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You definitely have some eye disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:05.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:06.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:09.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was only for a moment, but he didn't look like you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, dumb kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:11.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.54,0:07:14.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How to describe him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.04,0:07:17.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems like the kind of guy who'll end up as your average manager at some office branch in 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:19.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, totally plain?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:23.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Middle school girls can sure run their mouths.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:27.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you get all quiet, Kirino?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:29.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:35.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:43.65,note,,0000,0000,0000,,To: Kousaka Kyousuke \NFrom: Makashima Saori
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:45.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:49.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:53.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That box!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:55.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:58.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it have my name—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:01.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an "Eternal" box!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:01.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:03.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:05.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:06.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:07.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:10.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I can't buy any of their stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.68,0:08:12.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:13.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No choice then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:15.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:20.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're even for that unnecessary stress you caused me with your screwup earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:22.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I mea—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:27.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:30.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kyousuke? It's me, Saori.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:31.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get my package?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:34.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:37.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the cosmetics maker box you sent?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:38.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:44.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I know Miss Kiririn's address and phone number, but I never asked what her real name was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:47.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you sent it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:50.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I gave it to her already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:51.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She looked very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:53.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:56.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're okay giving that brand of cosmetics to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:57.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that stuff really expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:09:03.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The contents of the box are completely unrelated to the box itself, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:04.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:07.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... what's inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:10.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What Miss Kiririn asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:13.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A Meruru and SisCaly doujinshi set.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:14.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:18.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ero stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:19.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To say the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:21.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you back later!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap this is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.72,0:09:32.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:34.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, barging in like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:37.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, there's been a mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:38.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:39.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:41.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you give me back that box?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:43.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You already gave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:45.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not making sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:47.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:51.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for interrupting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:53.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:56.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:57.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:09:58.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop making excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:05.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:08.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said no!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:15.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:18.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Die! Die die die die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:27.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:43.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, some eroge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:47.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirino?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:53.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah, you're in that kind of relationship with your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:56.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:56.09,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.02,0:11:05.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare come back inside until everyone's gone home, you freaking pervert!{FOTC: I think "freaking pervert" sounds more Kirino.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.40,0:11:12.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for having us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:27.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:33.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:38.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that box have something that Kirino shouldn't see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:44.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't feel like you were just trying to harass her earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:47.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You seemed desperate, trying your hardest...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:50.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought maybe there was a reason for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:53.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a present for her for some special day?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:56.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:58.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:12:00.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's some reason for it right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:07.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what it is, but please forgive Kirino!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:13.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a bit selfish, but I'm sure she doesn't actually hate you or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.05,0:12:15.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:17.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.26,0:12:18.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:21.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for looking out for her all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:23.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:25.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're best friends, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:32.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we got a chance to talk...{可愛いけど、何かズレてる... ヤンデシマエヨ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:39.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:41.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Kousaka Kyousuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:43.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:44.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the late introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:47.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Aragaki Ayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:50.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:51.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:02.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:03.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but couldn't you have done it some other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:04.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:08.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for just grabbing this and running to your room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:09.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you trying to blame me for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:15.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Things got this confusing because you went and secretly became friends with Saori!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:19.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,See, you're already distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:20.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:23.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And what was with you going all ga-ga for Ayase? {better wording lol}{I like that word.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:24.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't check out my friends like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:25.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:26.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're{\i0} calling {\i1}me{\i0} a pervert?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:31.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to take responsibility for embarrassing me in front of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:32.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:38.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be busy with my club this summer, so I won't be able to go out much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:40.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have training camp the second half of August, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:42.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:45.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically you want me to take you out somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:46.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the beach or the mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:50.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can go to those kinds of places with Ayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:52.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you want to go then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:54.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:14.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I have to get up so early and come to a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:17.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, after thinking about it, I asked her in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:21.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I proposed we make our Summer Comiket debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:24.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually already thinking of inviting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:27.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had some responsibility for the incident, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:29.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:31.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do I have to wait in line?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:32.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My feet hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:33.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No one cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:36.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit complaining and just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:38.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're annoying the people around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:47.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess this line is tough on first-timers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:50.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this. And you even lent us a chair...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:55.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, if she really didn't want to be here, she wouldn't have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:59.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess as her brother you know her quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:06.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot... Gross... Annoying...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:09.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please be quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:11.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're making the discomfort index go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.60,0:15:16.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But why do all these people line up for hours in this inferno for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they want doujinshi that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:24.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not everyone's here for the same thing, but I'm sure you'll understand once it begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:26.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When does it begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:32.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This year's Summer Comic Circle Market is now open!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:37.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enter calmly, and no pushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:49.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot... Loud... Smelly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:51.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a frail human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:54.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better than it was yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:55.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You came here yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:15:58.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually here two days ago too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:16:00.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A battle is something you stick with from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:03.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what's so fun about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:07.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer to that is right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:11.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Running is dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:13.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:21.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The ceiling's so high!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:28.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kiririn, did you have any artists you liked from the doujinshi I sent you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:37.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I had to choose, I'd say Yamanashi Ganma's Meruru book and QQQ's Reika book.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:39.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And... Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:44.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura G. Sakura did the artbook, right?\NShe's doing Meruru's comic version, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:47.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:48.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Total recovery!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:52.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, those books were all made by people I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:53.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:53.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:58.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of making my rounds to say hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:17:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to join me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.21,0:17:01.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Seriousl—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:05.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:07.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But only if you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:08.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do join me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:23.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit cooler because it's cloudy, but isn't it really harsh wearing a costume like that in summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:26.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's too hot, you stuff ice packs in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.82,0:17:29.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a drop of sweat on you either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:31.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You do things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:32.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:36.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I put up a thin curtain of dark energy which protects me from the sun and heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:38.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:40.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:42.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:46.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid you don't have the eyes of the "Children of the Night".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:48.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't possibly see dark energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:51.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And now you've turned all teen complex again.{jakigan}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:55.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're cosplaying again today? That Maschera character?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:57.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where exactly are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:59.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're totally wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:18:00.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,These are my normal clothes.{So lovely~~~~~~}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:04.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If these are your normal clothes, then you can make them a bit cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.94,0:18:07.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, don't—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:10.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:15.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said that this heat was nothing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:17.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, sure. Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:22.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You look pretty cute when you're not wearing those thick clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:26.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you stop giving compliments with your "I'm still better" attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:28.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? Getting embarrassed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:32.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:32.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:39.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,West Halls 3 and 4 are for industry booths.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:41.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:44.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want at the Alice+ booth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:48.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alice+? I've heard that name somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:49.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They made SisCaly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:54.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go ahead! I need to buy that Limited Edition Summer Comiket Disc!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Limited edition disc?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:59.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A collector's item with data for the new SisCaly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:02.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:04.33,Whiteboard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(738,362)\frz356\c&H555ca0&}Sold \NOut
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:09.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You would have needed to line up as soon as it opened to buy it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:10.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:13.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:15.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you couldn't really help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:17.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:19.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:24.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... there's one disc left...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.65,0:19:35.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you can get the disc if you can beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:37.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds interesting. I'll give it a go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:45.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That staff member's won 50 straight games these last three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:46.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't plan to let anyone win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:49.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's also a high-ranking player on the PC version.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:51.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you give him an unanalyzed new character...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:56.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:57.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn this crappy game!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:19:59.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I could win!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:00.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's such a ripoff!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:04.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... you weren't great at Siscalypse to begin with...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:05.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Saori is much bette—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:09.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My deepest apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:12.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:14.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, no one's winning that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:19.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:20.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Naive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:34.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:36.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:37.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:42.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And you call yourself a little sister? How silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:48.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuroneko-dono!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:49.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:52.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea you were so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.61,0:20:53.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stifling...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:54.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you stop that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:03.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:06.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:10.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:12.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You don't want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:15.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe you don't understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:17.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want it then throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:20.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I didn't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:22.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not just accept it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:25.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is my beauty overwhelming you? {check}{Fine to me.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:26.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a boring human.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:28.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is everything you say so annoying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:31.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see a single speck of beauty anywhere on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:32.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She just can't be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:34.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed... both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:37.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well if you insist, I'll take it off your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:38.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Be grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:44.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.42,0:22:01.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Comiket can certainly be pretty harsh, but if you put your all into it, you can find all sorts of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.22,0:22:04.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I figured we should come here together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.18,0:22:06.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.68,0:22:10.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it has nothing to do with a normal person like me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:13.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you give me back my coat now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.11,0:22:18.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.52,0:22:19.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.73,0:22:21.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What might you be talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:26.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.82,0:22:28.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirino!
