Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:25.00,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,そんな優しくしないで　どんな顔すればいいの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:33.80,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,積み重ねた言葉で　見えないよ　きみの横顔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:47.53,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,どこだっけ？　なくした鍵は見つからないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:54.28,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,ため息　すれ違いに意地張って　疲れちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.28,0:01:00.91,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,ほんの少し近く　きみとの距離が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:08.17,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,うまく掴めないんだ　あとちょっとなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:15.14,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,そんな優しくしないで　ほらまた傷つけあって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.14,0:01:22.14,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,積み重ねた嘘でも　動けなくなってる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:29.57,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,すぐに合いに行きたいけど　言葉は見つからないし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:39.75,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,最後の一ページかい？　きみには笑顔見せたい
Comment: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Romaji}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:25.00,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,sonna yasashiku shinai de donna kao sureba ii no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:33.80,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,tsumikasaneta kotoba de mienaiyo kimi no yokogao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:47.53,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,dokodakke? nakushita kagi ha mitsukaranai mama de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:54.28,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,tameiki surechigai ni iji hatte tsukarechau
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.28,0:01:00.91,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,hon no sukoshi chikaku kimi to no kyori ga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:08.17,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,umaku tsukamenainda ato chotto na no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:15.14,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,sonna yasashikushinaide hora mata kizutsukeatte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.14,0:01:22.14,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,tsumikasaneta uso demo ugokenakunatteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:29.57,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,sugu ni ai ni ikitai kedo kotoba ha mitsukaranai shi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:39.75,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,saigo no ichi pe-ji kai? kimi ni ha egao misetai
Comment: 0,0:00:17.04,0:00:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Translation}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:25.00,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so nice to me, I just don't know how to react
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:33.80,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,With all these words piling up, I can't even see your face
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:47.53,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it? I lost my key, now I can't find it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:54.28,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Sigh, I'll burn out if I keep acting like this whenever we miss
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.28,0:01:00.91,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we're close? I just can't figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:08.17,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how far away I am, even though you're right there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:15.14,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so nice to me, see? We hurt each other again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.14,0:01:22.14,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,With all these lies piling up, I can't even move
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:29.57,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you now, but I don't know what to say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:39.75,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the end for our story? I want you to see my smile
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:44.59,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,強く強く　願っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.93,0:22:51.81,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,あなたが隠す本当の笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:22:59.15,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,遠く遠く　見受けたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:07.24,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,私から伝えるさよなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.41,0:23:21.38,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,あなたが本当に大切にしたいもの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:29.05,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,一つだけじゃないって分かっていたいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:36.77,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ　お願い私だけを見つめ続けてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.14,0:23:43.73,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,かき乱されぬ汚れなき心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.03,0:23:50.70,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,出来るなら認めたい(認められない)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.70,0:23:55.75,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,白いキャンバスに描がかれたとも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.96,0:24:02.75,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,全て背負って生きて行くの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:44.59,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,tsuyoku tsuyoku negatteita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.93,0:22:51.81,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,anata ga kakusu hontou no egao
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:22:59.15,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,tooku tooku miuketai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:07.24,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,watashi kara tsutaeru sayonara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.41,0:23:21.38,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,anata ga hontou ni taisetsu ni shitai mono
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:29.05,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,hitotsu dake janaitte wakatteitai kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:36.77,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,ne onegai watashi dake wo mitsumetsudzukete yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.14,0:23:43.73,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,kakimidasarenu kegarenaki kokoro
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.03,0:23:50.70,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,dekiru nara mitometai (mitomerarenai)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.70,0:23:55.75,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,shiroi kyanbasu ni egakareta tomo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.96,0:24:02.75,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,subete seotte ikiteyuku no
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:44.59,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Strongly, strongly, I wished
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.93,0:22:51.81,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,To see the true smile you’re hiding
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:22:59.15,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,From afar, from afar, I want to see
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:07.24,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,A goodbye from me to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.41,0:23:21.38,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,I try to understand that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:29.05,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,You hold more than one thing dear
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:36.77,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,But please, just look only at me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.14,0:23:43.73,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,With your pure, incorruptible heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.03,0:23:50.70,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to accept it (I cannot accept it)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.70,0:23:55.75,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if drawn on white canvas
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.96,0:24:02.75,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll undertake it all and live on {Get the pun? やんデレあやせ楽しみ〜}
